    m_HorizontalOverflow: 0
    m_VerticalOverflow: 0
    m_LineSpacing: 1.1
  m_Text: "<color=black><size=45>Play Mechanics</size></color>\nTap to release balls
    onto the Plinko board.\nWatch as they ricochet through pegs to land in point-value
    slots.\n\n<color=black><size=45>Earning System</size></color>\nAutomatically
    collect \"Diamonds\" based on:\n  \u2713 Ball landing positions\n  \u2713 Your
    gameplay activity\nReward updates: Cash calculations occur every 3 hours using
    your Diamond balance.\nPro Tip: Maximize earnings by active participation and
    targeting high-value slots.\n\n<color=black><size=45>Easy Withdrawals</size></color>\nDirectly
    transfer earnings to your registered account via supported payment methods.\nIndustry-low
    threshold: Start withdrawals at just $0.10!\n\n<color=black><size=45>Important
    Notice</size></color>\nEnsure your withdrawal details are accurate for seamless
    payment processing.\n\n<color=black><size=45>Customer Support</size></color>\nNeed
    assistance or have inquiries?\nContact our team: "
